title: Miami-Fort Lauderdale-West Palm Beach metro area population U.S. 2010 to 2018
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Number of residents. In total the number of data points it has is 9.
In general Number of residents has rose over the Year.
Number of residents is slightly increasing from 2010 to 2018.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2010 and 2011.
The highest Number of residents, of value 6198782.0 was reached at Year 2018
The lowest Number of residents, of value 5583547.0 was reported at Year 2010
